Package: hoo
Title: Calculate adjacency vectors using horizon of observation model
Version: 3.0
Authors@R: person("Shengyang", "Cao", email = "scaotravis@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package contains function "horizon" suitable for multimodal analysis under Hutchins' horizon of observation model. The adjacency vectors are calculated so that it can be used under ENA analysis (see "rENA" package for more information). 
Imports:
    tidyr, 
    stats
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
